{
    "_doc": "Rival Soldier — guards a rival king. Faction 'rival' so player/ally ContactDamage (targetFactions ['enemy','rival']) targets it; itself targets ['player','ally','structure'] so it attacks the player + allied soldiers but ignores zombies and other rival units. Stats from balance.json combat.rival_soldier.* — HP 75 (between Scout 50 and Bruiser 125), damage 10 (= sword), cooldown 1.0. HeroAI with guardRadius keeps it near its spawn (next to the king). Placeholder for next-session worker-spawned soldier — for now placed directly in level-prototype.json next to each rival king.",
    "type": "RivalSoldier",
    "mesh": {
        "preset": "character-soldier",
        "color":  "0xb02828",
        "weapon": "sword"
    },
    "components": {
